        <li class="skill-ball ball-4 fade-in">
          <%= image_tag("html.png", class: "html-pic") %>
        </li>
        <li class="skill-ball ball-5 fade-in">
          <%= image_tag("javascript.png", class: "java-pic") %>
        </li>
        <li class="skill-ball ball-6 fade-in">
          <%= image_tag("ruby.png", class: "ruby-pic") %>
        </li>
        <li class="skill-ball ball-7 fade-in">
          <%= image_tag("bootstrap.png", class: "boot-pic") %>
        </li>
        <li class="skill-ball ball-8 fade-in">
          <%= image_tag("postgresql.png", class: "post-pic") %>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="col-5">
      <div class="skill-right-title">
        <h2>My story</h2>
      </div>
      <br>
      <div class="container skill-right-para">
        <p>Before discovering coding and the world of web development I had studied finance and worked for a start up in sales. While I enjoyed both of these experiences and learned from them both I knew that I wanted to do something else with my life. I ended up moving to Paris after I left my job and discovered coding through a friend. I began taking lessons online and quickly became obsessed with it. After a few months learning on my own I decided to enroll in Le Wagon, Europes top coding bootcamp. This was a life changing experience and taught me exactly what I want to do with my life. Outside of web development I enjoy skateboarding, surfing, and traveling.</p>
